      "body" : "Useful answer! However, the last sentence &quot;Locale-based formatting is preferred, though&quot; does not make sense without context. There are pretty good use cases where you should NOT use locale-based formatting, when you want to generate a specific format of the String. E.g. you are implementing export of your data to an external file and you want to have full control over the format, not dependent on the current (or any) locale."
