    "body" : "<p>If you want to format it with manually set symbols, use this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>DecimalFormatSymbols decimalFormatSymbols = new DecimalFormatSymbols();\ndecimalFormatSymbols.setDecimalSeparator('.');\ndecimalFormatSymbols.setGroupingSeparator(',');\nDecimalFormat decimalFormat = new DecimalFormat(\"#,##0.00\", decimalFormatSymbols);\nSystem.out.println(decimalFormat.format(1237516.2548)); //1,237,516.25\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Locale-based formatting is preferred, though.</p>\n"
